from Safe Harbors,
the company that built it.

30:38.087 --> 30:41.170
Oh, good, that should indicate
an escape hatch that would
override the time lock.

30:41.257 --> 30:44.670
Yeah, you’d think so,
but they said the emergency
routes and hatches...

30:44.760 --> 30:48.469
