and giving them out would
compromise security.

30:48.556 --> 30:51.514
There’s gotta be some kind
of exit in case of a fire
or other disaster.

30:51.600 --> 30:53.932
I mean, surviving
is kind of the point
of the bunker.

30:54.020 --> 30:57.808
Yeah, well, that’s why I’m
doing a structural analysis
of the plans.

