with that grade of steel.

31:23.299 --> 31:27.212
Which means there’s
a section of the frame
which isn’t category 1.

31:27.303 --> 31:31.342
Yeah. If we can find it, we can find
the escape hatch the killer used...

31:31.432 --> 31:34.515
