at the murder scene.

37:57.901 --> 37:59.812
You did it.
You loaded the dragon’s breath.

37:59.903 --> 38:02.610
Either you were mad
that she slept
with your husband—

38:02.698 --> 38:05.861
— Or that she gave him syphilis.
— Or maybe even gave it to you.

38:07.327 --> 38:09.909
The object was to survive.

38:09.997 --> 38:12.238
My husband and I
devoted our lives to that.

38:12.332 --> 38:16.666
Deanna was aggressive,
overbearing, dishonest.

38:16.753 --> 38:19.790
Is that someone you want with
you when you build a new world?

38:19.882 --> 38:21.747
Well, I’m not sure about that.

38:21.842 --> 38:25.209
But I certainly wouldn’t
want someone like you
deciding that for me.

38:28.098 --> 38:31.886
The world is going to end
because of people like her.

